latestIgtvVideos.caption:
In light of the current situation going on Instagram I felt the need to write down this poem and present it in spoken word form. However, keep in mind that this message is very general and not as specific, hinting towards not exactly one situation.

PLEASE SHARE... MAKE PEACE NOT WAR (I have also posted this video on my Youtube Channel, link in bio)

latestIgtvVideos.title: The Traveler: the journey of a lost heart.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
While I was going back to Patiala, I looked out the window and saw fields of flowers that were unknown to me, so the curious little child that lives inside me pointed out and asked her mother, and the moment she told me that they were marigold, the inspiration came instantly. So here it is "The Traveler". Hope you enjoy it. -

#voetry #poetry #travellogs #travelling #trains #poems #poemsofinstagram #marigold #videopoetry #blackandwhite #poetsofinstgram
